videos.description: Grant Williams strips the ball from TJ Starks, and Jordan Bone takes it the other way, pulling up to sink the midrange jumper in transition.
videos.headline: Williams steals, Bone scores

videos.description: Josh Nebo misses his initial layup attempt, but springs right back up to the rim and cleans up the miss with a thunderous two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Nebo throws down putback jam on two Tennessee defenders

videos.description: Jordan Bone throws over the zone to Kyle Alexander, who elevates and finishes with a rim-rocking dunk that quiets the crowd.
videos.headline: Alexander hammers down one-handed slam

videos.description: Texas A&M has no answer for Grant Williams in the post, as the Tennessee big man drops 22 points to lead the Vols to a 93-76 win over the Aggies.
